A year ago today we were we were massively honoured to host the wedding of Martin & Joanna King, who met at The Lacehouse a few years before.

It was a monumental effort from the whole team to transform the venue overnight - from a busy bar shift on Friday, to a beauutiful wedding venue on Saturday morning, but it was worth every second to see so many happy faces!

If you have a birthday, corporate function or wedding coming up then we'd love to hear from you.  Send us a message on Facebook & let us help your dream party idea become reality.

Happy Anniversary to The Kings! x
